ation on his
legislative agenda and, especially, on midterm races=E2=80=94even if Trump =
often followed his own gut instincts. Stepien recently came on my podcast, =
Somebody=E2=80=99s Gotta Win, to talk about Trump=E2=80=99s unusual relatio=
nship with political capital, how that will dictate the legislative fights =
ahead, and which cabinet appointments he thinks Trump will actually fight f=
