=C2=A0

If he doesn=E2=80=99t, it=E2=80=99s their job to help him understand if the=
y want to be successful. The stakes are so high on this. And I think Johnso=
n, in particular, has carved out a great relationship with Trump. It=E2=80=
=99s their job to make sure he is involved and engaged, and if he=E2=80=99s=
 not, just ask Mitch McConnell how that goes.

