crats. But that=E2=80=99s where the slim majority comes in. Then you have C=
hristmas and the holidays, and you=E2=80=99ve got January 20 coming up arou=
nd the corner pretty fast. At the same time, Trump=E2=80=99s focused on the=
 cabinet and getting his people in place and assembling a government. So
there are a ton of competing interests when it comes to time. How long one =
