f balls in the air that make things complicated.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;ma=
rgin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;">They=E2=80=99re almost c=
ertainly going to lose the House; history tells us that, especially with a =
slim majority. So you=E2=80=99ve got one term in front of you, and you=E2=
=80=99ve got two years before you probably lose control of the House. That=
=E2=80=99s why he=E2=80=99s
been so aggressive in trying to get his people in place in the cabinet, bec=
ause he understands that, unlike 2017, when he was walking in the door with=
